%S A396719 1,14,142,1774,23694,327406,4576142,64239182,903148878,12704455886,
%T A396719 178746165646,2515054013614,35389018388238,497958891998638,
%U A396719 7006801408176782,98593118117783054,1387310152608203214,19520933742401185166,274680374985035619982,3865046145727031148142
%N A396719 Volume (in unit cubes) of the level-n additive cube fractal in which a central cube of side 2*Pell(n-1) is surrounded by six copies of the previous level (silver-ratio scaling).
%C A396719 The fractal is built additively: level 1 is a solid unit cube; to pass from level n-1 to level n one takes a solid central cube of side s(n) = 2*Pell(n-1) and attaches a complete copy of level n-1 to each of its six faces, the shared junction cube being counted once. a(n) is the solid volume of level n, measured in unit (seed) cubes.
%C A396719 The number of unit cubes at level n is A057651(n-1) = (3*5^(n-1)-1)/2, and the total side length is 2*Pell(n) = 2*A000129(n). The ratio between consecutive levels tends to the silver ratio 1 + sqrt(2).
%H A396719 <a href="/index/Rec#order_05">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (17,-30,-162,59,5).
%F A396719 a(1) = 1; a(n) = 5*a(n-1) + s(n)^3 + s(n-1)^3, where s(1) = 1 and s(n) = 2*A000129(n-1) for n >= 2.
%F A396719 a(n) = 17*a(n-1) - 30*a(n-2) - 162*a(n-3) + 59*a(n-4) + 5*a(n-5) for n >= 7.
%F A396719 G.f.: x*(1 + x)*(1 + 6*x - x^2)*(1 - 10*x - x^2)/((1 - 5*x)*(1 + 2*x - x^2)*(1 - 14*x - x^2)).
%e A396719 The recurrence a(n) = 5*a(n-1) + s(n)^3 + s(n-1)^3 uses the central-cube side s(n) = 2*Pell(n-1) = 1, 2, 4, 10, 24, ... :
%e A396719 a(2) = 5*a(1) + s(2)^3 + s(1)^3 = 5*1 + 2^3 + 1^3 = 14.
%e A396719 a(3) = 5*a(2) + s(3)^3 + s(2)^3 = 5*14 + 4^3 + 2^3 = 142.
%e A396719 a(4) = 5*a(3) + s(4)^3 + s(3)^3 = 5*142 + 10^3 + 4^3 = 1774.
%t A396719 Join[{1}, LinearRecurrence[{17, -30, -162, 59, 5}, {14, 142, 1774, 23694, 327406, 4576142}, 19]]
%o A396719 (PARI) Vec(x*(1 - 3*x - 66*x^2 - 58*x^3 + 5*x^4 + x^5)/(1 - 17*x + 30*x^2 + 162*x^3 - 59*x^4 - 5*x^5) + O(x^21))
%Y A396719 Cf. A000129, A052542, A057651.
%K A396719 nonn,easy,new
%O A396719 1,2
